4.1 Agenda
==========

Casual Agenda is a user interface for Org Agenda.  Its top-level library
is ‚Äòcasual-agenda‚Äô.

Configuration
=============

The main menu for Casual Agenda is the Transient menu
‚Äòcasual-agenda-tmenu‚Äô.  Bind this menu in the keymap
‚Äòorg-agenda-mode-map‚Äô as follows in your initialization file.

     (keymap-set org-agenda-mode-map "C-o" #'casual-agenda-tmenu)

